{"title":"DIALLO Amadou | Portfolio","markdown":{"headingText":"<div class=\"page-home\">","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"title: \"DIALLO Amadou | Portfolio\"\nbody-class: home-page\n---\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 30px; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n\n<img src=\"images/profile.jpg\" style=\"width: 160px; height: 160px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px;\" />\n\n<div>\n\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"cv/amadou_diallo_cv.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" \nstyle=\"display: inline-block; margin-top: 10px; padding: 8px 14px; background-color: #1d4ed8; color: white; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;\">\nDownload Resume\n</a>\n</p>\n\n\n# DIALLO Amadou  \n### Junior Data Scientist | ML Engineer | Applied Research Engineer\n\nApplied Machine Learning and Data Science profile with a strong mathematical background.\n\nI build robust predictive models, interpretable ML systems, and research-oriented pipelines for complex data.\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## About Me\n\nCurrently completing an M2 in Data Mathematics after a first master's degree in Algebra and Applications, I specialize in Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Data Science, and Topological Data Analysis (TDA).\n\nMy work combines business-oriented ML projects (churn prediction, risk modeling) with research-driven approaches involving high-dimensional data and topology-aware representations.\n\n---\n\n## What I Do\n\n### Data Science & Predictive Modeling\nDesign and evaluation of predictive models with a strong focus on data quality, feature engineering, and business-oriented metrics.\n\n### Machine Learning & Pipelines\nDevelopment of end-to-end ML workflows using scikit-learn pipelines, model tuning, and reproducible experimentation.\n\n### Applied Research & Complex Data\nWork on high-dimensional data using topology-aware methods (TDA), representation learning, and hybrid ML approaches.\n\n---\n\n## Featured Work\n\n### COVID-19 Diagnostic Prediction\nBinary classification model to predict SARS-CoV-2 positivity using clinical and biological data.\n\n[View Project](https://github.com/DialloAmo/covid_analysis)\n\n---\n\n### Customer Churn Prediction *(Work in Progress)*\nPredict customer churn and derive actionable business insights.\n\n[View Project](https://github.com/DialloAmo/Customer_Churn_Prediction)\n\n---\n\n## Contact\n\n📧 [amadoudiallodjikesse@gmail.com](mailto:amadoudiallodjikesse@gmail.com)\n🔗 [GitHub](https://github.com/DialloAmo)\n🔗 [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/amadou-diallo-454270238)\n\n</div>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["styles.css"],"toc":false,"output-file":"index.html"},"l